**  ER (ERROR-MESSAGE)
E-01 NO FINAL SETTING NUMBER ENTRY
E-02 EACH FACTORY IS BILLED.
E-03 NO K-TYPE(S) ENTRY
E-04 NO ENTRY IN REVERSING DEPARTMENT TYPE
E-05 NO SETTING CODE ENTRY
E-06 SETTING CODE MUST BE NUMERICAL
E-07 NO USER'S NUM.OF DEL.ENTRY
E-08 USER'S NUM.OF DEL.MUST BE EQUAL TO OR UNDER NUM.
E-09 K-TYPE(S) A;USER'S NUM.OF DEL. MUST BE 5 OR OVER 5.
E-10 K-TYPE(S) B;USER'S NUM.OF DEL. MUST BE 4 OR UNDER 4.
E-11 NO BOX TYPE-1 ENTRY
E-12 NO BOX TYPE-2 ENTRY
E-13 NO QUANTITY IN CONTAINER ENTRY
E-14 QUANTITY IN CONTAINER UNIT ENTRY
E-15 NUMBER OF KANBAN'S MUST BE EQUAL TO OR UNDER 90000
E-16 OBSOLETE KANBAN DATA, REMAKE REQUIRED
E-17 WRONG LOCATION
E-18 NO DATA IN KANBAN TYPE M/F
E-19 NO VENDOR DEPOARTMENT DATA IN BAR CODE M/F
E-20 NO DATA IN DEPATMENTAL LT M/F
E-21 NO DATA IN SETTING M/F
E-22 NO DATA IN CONDITION M/F
E-23 DUPLICATION OCCURRED IN REVERSING CONDITION CODE
E-24 WRONG NUMBER OF BOXES ENTRY
E-25 EACH AOYAMA FACTORY IS RECEIVING FACTORY
E-26 ENTER RECEIVING POINT.
E-27 NUMBER REQUIRED ALONG WITH COMPONENT PART NO.
E-28 COMPONENT PART NO. REQUIRED ALONG WITH NUMBER
E-29 UPDATE EFFECTIVE DATA DUE TO CHANGE IN KANBAN'S DETAILS
E-30 MAX #OF BOXS DIFFERENT W SAFETY INVENTORY
